Run these commands on the FNAL gpvms.

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/njlane314/generators.git
cd generators

Start the uboone container before building:

./.container.sh

Build the generator stack inside the container:

./build_generators.sh

This builds GENIE v3.6.0, GiBUU 2025, NuWro 21.09.2, nusystematics, HepMC3, and NUISANCE.

Set up the environment in each new shell:

cd /path/to/generators
source setup_generators.sh

The setup script configures the generator paths and requests a uboone token.

Run the example jobcards:

cd example
./run_all.sh

If the GENIE spline XML is missing or stale, regenerate it before running gevgen:

gmkspl -p 14 -t 1000180400 -e 10. \
  -o example/samples/14_1000180400_CC_v3_6_2_AR23_20i_00_000.xml \
  --tune AR23_20i_00_000 --event-generator-list CC

Regenerate the XML when the probe, target, interaction list, GENIE tune/model setup, or energy coverage changes.
